The paper deals with enhancing underwater images using machine learning techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The use of adversarial learning to disentangle unwanted nuisances corresponds to domain adaptation (cs.MM) and domain generalization (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the improvement in object detection, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
